See https://stackoverflow.com/a/43389508

> If you want to keep using pysftp, do not set cnopts.hostkeys = None (as the second most upvoted answer shows), unless you do not care about security. You lose a protection against [Man-in-the-middle attacks](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Man-in-the-middle_attack) by doing so.
